 training including video and scenario-based exercises across different equipment types. Hone your skills and be ready for whatever the real world throws at you.\n\nWhether you\u2019re new on the job or a more seasoned pro looking to advance, the course catalog can help you be the kind of tech you want to be \u2013 a great one.\n\nA growing catalog of field-like training courses focused on helping tradesmen upskill through:\nInteractive, 3D based simulations to deliver field-like training\nExpert-led video courses drive understanding\nKnowledge checks throughout engage users and reinforce lessons\n\nTrailer music: https://www.bensound.com", "short_description": "VR training simulations develop on-the-job skills quickly and efficiently, building better careers and better lives for the essential skilled trades."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://www.interplaylearning.com/privacy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "https://www.interplaylearning.com/terms-of-use", "publisher_name": "Interplay Learning Inc", "support_website_url": "https://www.interplaylearning.com/contact", "website_url": "https://www.interplaylearning.com/", "category": "APPS", "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "362692211442873", "context_category": "APPS"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "514087707868786"}, {"id": "1043107547362485"}], "external_subscription_type": "REQUIRED", "genres": ["EDUCATIONAL", "SIMULATION"], "has_in_app_ads": null, "internet_connection": "REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "337040224979551"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 1, "nodes": [{"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "331463585266126"}]}, "baseline_offer": {"